📝 Be Clear and Specific
Provide detailed context in prompts for better results.

🧩 Break Down Complex Tasks
Ask step-by-step instead of one giant request.

🔄 Iterate and Refine
Treat it like a conversation — improve with follow-ups.

📊 Use Examples
Share preferred formats or styles to guide responses.

✅ Validate Outputs
Always review, test, and fact-check generated content.

🎭 Set Roles & Context
Start with “You are an expert…” for tailored responses.

✂️ Stay Concise
Keep prompts focused, avoid unnecessary details.

🎨 Adjust Creativity (Temperature)
Low = factual, High = creative/varied.
